    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with every component functioning perfectly and a complete, documented service history. This is a collector-grade example that has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
