    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to a standard that defies its tenure. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting a level of preservation that is virtually indistinguishable from its original showroom state. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship and an uncompromising commitment to excellence, offering a driving experience tailored for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
