      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one! Not a scratch, the interior still has that new car smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I do. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
